sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant MessagingService
    participant AuthenticationService
    participant GroupService
    participant MonitoringSystem

    User->>MessagingService: Send message
    MessagingService-->>User: Acknowledge message receipt
    MessagingService->>MonitoringSystem: Check uptime status
    MonitoringSystem-->>MessagingService: Uptime is within SLA

    User->>AuthenticationService: Request authentication
    AuthenticationService-->>User: Provide authentication token
    AuthenticationService->>MonitoringSystem: Check uptime status
    MonitoringSystem-->>AuthenticationService: Uptime is within SLA

    User->>GroupService: Join group
    GroupService-->>User: Confirm group membership
    GroupService->>MonitoringSystem: Check uptime status
    MonitoringSystem-->>GroupService: Uptime is within SLA